snippet.title: Hexual Deflection - Multiplayer Tower Defense/Attack
snippet.description:
Multiplayer Tower Defense Gameplay - like Tower Defense, but you also attack!

Play against 16+ Players. Make your own Maps, Play against friends. Minimalistic RTS Experience, as there is only 3 Buildings:

Defend
Attack
Ressources

That's it - are you ready for the chaos? Beat them all and take the victory

Wishlist now on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2975730/Hexual_Deflection/
